Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:33.86,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,坐下来苦想是没有用的 宝贝 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:39.48,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,你至今还是没能弄清 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:48.53,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,坐下来苦想是没有用的 宝贝 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:53.55,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,怎么着也不会有用了 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:01:02.16,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,天色破晓 公鸡开始啼鸣 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:05.70,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,你朝窗外看去{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.95,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,而我已经走远{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:15.50,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,让我重回旅途的缘故在于你 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:21.22,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,不过不必多想了 这没什么 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:29.18,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,打开你的那盏灯是没有用的 宝贝 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:34.86,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,我从未见识过的那盏灯 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:43.98,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,打开你的那盏灯是没有用的 宝贝 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:49.22,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,此刻我身处路途的暗面 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:57.23,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,可是我依然渴望你能有所行动 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:05.18,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,来让我回心转意 留下别走 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:10.98,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,我们过去交流实在太少了 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:16.24,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,不过不必多想了 这没什么 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:21.56,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,呼唤我的名字也是没有用的 亲爱的 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.85,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,从前你可没这样做过 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:35.52,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,呼唤我的名字也是没有用的 亲爱的 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:40.76,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,我已经什么也听不见了 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:50.00,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,一路上我在思考着一个问题 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:57.07,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,我曾经爱上一个男人 我说他是个孩子 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:04:03.86,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,我交出了我的心 他却想要我的灵魂 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:08.88,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,所以不必多想了 这没什么 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:16.77,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,再见了 亲爱的 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:23.20,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,去往何方 我不能讲 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:32.73,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,但是“拜拜”这词太过甜美 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:37.63,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,我还是说“别了”为好 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:46.02,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,我不想说你过去对我不好 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:53.66,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,你可以做得更好的 但也没事儿了 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:59.68,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,你有点在浪费我宝贵的时间 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:05.20,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,不必多想了 这没什么 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.64,0:05:12.41,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,不必多想了 这没什么 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:20.22,白色中文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,不必多想了 这没什么 {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:33.86,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,It ain't no use to sit and wonder why, babe{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:39.48,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,Even you don't know by now{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.85,0:00:48.53,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,An' it ain't no use to sit and wonder why, babe{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.78,0:00:53.55,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,It don't matter anyhow{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:01:02.16,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,When your rooster crows at the break of dawn{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:05.70,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,Look out your window {\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.95,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,I'll be gone{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:15.50,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,You're the reason I'm trav'lin' on{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:21.22,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,Don't think twice, it's all right{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.27,0:01:29.18,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,It ain't no use in turnin' on your light, babe{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:34.86,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,That light I never knowed{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.94,0:01:43.98,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,An' it ain't no use in turnin' on your light, babe{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.87,0:01:49.22,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm on the dark side of the road{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:57.23,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,but I wish there was somethin' you would do or say{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:05.18,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,To try and make me change my mind and stay{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:10.98,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,We never did too much talkin' anyway{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.67,0:02:16.24,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,So don't think twice, it's all right{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:21.56,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,It ain't no use in callin' out my name, gal{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.29,0:03:26.85,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,Like you never did before{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:35.52,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,It ain't no use in callin' out my name, gal{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:40.76,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you any more{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:50.00,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,I'm a-thinkin' and a-wond'rin' walkin’ down the road{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.34,0:03:57.07,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,I once loved a man, a child I'm told{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.31,0:04:03.86,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,I gave him my heart but he wanted my soul{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:08.88,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,So don't think twice, it's all right{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:16.77,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,So long, Honey Babe{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:23.20,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,Where I'm bound, I can't tell{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:32.73,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,But goodbye's too good a word, gal{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:37.63,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,So I'll just say fare thee well{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:46.02,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,I ain't sayin' you treated me unkind{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:53.66,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,You could have done better but I don't mind{\fad(1,500)}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:59.68,白色英文歌词1080p,,0,0,0,,You just kinda wasted my precious time{\fad(1,500)}
